## Key Features Implementation
- StreamPanel: URL inputs, status dots, Go Live controls, timer
- TranscriptionPanel: Live transcript, vote extraction, simulation
- ResultsPanel: Form upload, OCR scanning, IEBC portal integration
- ComparisonPanel: Three-source comparison, discrepancy detection
- AlertsPanel: Real-time alerts, escalate/dismiss actions
- Public dashboard: National results table, Kenya map
- Admin panel: Campaign oversight and management
